Quote: A friend rang up and by way of extolling the virues of noni juice began: "You know I can be a cruel, ruthless bastard ..." Well, he continued, he'd been taking noni juice for a month now. He pissed like a fire hydrant, he felt boundless energy, his blood pressure count had dropped; he dropped his voice as he came to the relevant part, the bit he thought would interest me "And my hair's grown back." I thought, "You cruel, ruthless bastard."
